Ayushmann Khurrana is currently being taught Bengali by two teachers for his next film, 'Meri Pyari Bindu' where he plays an urban Bengali gentleman from Kolkata.
He is paired opposite Parineeti Chopra in the movie which is primarily shot in Kolkata.
